      ["Clone the eligible cohort into the strategy arms and apply the censoring rule.", "Fit the censoring model(s) and compute stabilised, time-varying IPCW.", "Fit a weighted pooled logistic regression for the discrete-time hazard, with the assigned strategy, follow-up time, its quadratic term, and a strategy × time interaction; derive weighted cumulative-incidence curves.", "Contrast the curves for the effect measure(s); 95% CIs by nonparametric bootstrap."].forEach((l) => children.push(numItem(l)));
      children.push(para("Comparison — conventional analysis (as-started, ITT-analogue): start follow-up at the index date, balance the arms by propensity-score matching (standardised mean difference < 0.1), and handle the competing risk of death with Fine–Gray sub-distribution and cause-specific Cox models."));

      children.push(h1("10. Subgroup analyses"));
